Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:39.52,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我为了不让其毁坏而太过于珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:45.44,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也输入邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:51.31,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又将其删除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.71,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这样的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.88,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将其打破的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}为我带来契机的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:04.70,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心将其紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.28,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将现在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.77,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}虽然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.64,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使将碎片全部收集齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必须用自己的双手将其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.54,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}极其珍视的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.89,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕将其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:30.58,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的这一切
